  <title>GLib.idle_source_new</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function idle_source_new(): <link xref="GLib.Source">GLib.Source</link> {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_idle_source_new()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Creates a new idle source.</p>  <p>The source will not initially be associated with any <link xref="GLib.MainContext"/>
and must be added to one with <link xref="GLib.Source.attach"/> before it will be
executed. Note that the default priority for idle sources is
%G_PRIORITY_DEFAULT_IDLE, as compared to other sources which
have a default priority of %G_PRIORITY_DEFAULT.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>the newly-created idle source</p>
</item>
